Assumptions:

(a1, (~x == #5))
(a2, (~y == #2)) (f1, (∀ ((~Int.Gt (~f %0)) %0)))
Proof Obligation:
((~Int.Gt ~x) ~y)

Label: use_f1
Assumptions:

(a1, (~x == #5))
(a2, (~y == #2)) (f1, (∀ ((~Int.Gt (~f %0)) %0)))
Proof Obligation:
((~Int.Gt (~f ((~Int.Add ~x) ~y))) #7)

Label: use_a1_again
Assumptions:

(a1, (~x == #5))
(a2, (~y == #2)) (f1, (∀ ((~Int.Gt (~f %0)) %0)))
Proof Obligation:
(~y == #2)

Label: use_a2_again
Assumptions:

(a1, (~x == #5))
(a2, (~y == #2)) (f1, (∀ ((~Int.Gt (~f %0)) %0)))
Proof Obligation:
((~Int.Gt (~f ~y)) ~y)

